sql_json.natural_language: Get the latest email from brendan@lightco.co.za that mentions ‘quote’.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE fromEmail = 'brendan@lightco.co.za' AND 'quote' IN UNNEST(searchTerms) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
